    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for a Class II device at MRL 2. CFD predictions of normalized index of hemolysis agree with experimental data within combined uncertainty at all 5 CPB operating points. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied for the nominal geometry. The model is accepted as fit for purpose for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use.",
